title: Dan Osborne
text:
Daniel James Osborne (born 27 June 1991) is an English television personality, known for being a former cast member on the <a href="ITVBe">ITVBe</a> reality series "<a href="The%20Only%20Way%20Is%20Essex">The Only Way Is Essex</a>". In 2018, he was a housemate on "<a href="Celebrity%20Big%20Brother%20%28British%20series%2022%29">Celebrity Big Brother</a>," reaching the final and finishing in third place.
Personal life.
Osborne is married to actress <a href="Jacqueline%20Jossa">Jacqueline Jossa</a>, with whom he has two daughters; Ella (born 2015) and Mia (born 2018). He also has a son, Teddy (born 2013) from an earlier relationship.
